1
00:00:30,739 --> 00:00:34,951
UNA FAMILIA ATÍPICA

2
00:01:42,435 --> 00:01:43,436
Has venido.

3
00:01:55,949 --> 00:01:57,200
No pienso dárselas.

4
00:01:58,284 --> 00:01:59,494
Y no la abrazaré

5
00:02:00,537 --> 00:02:01,996
